>> title: Italian Roasted Vegetables
>> cuisine: Italian
>> tags: vegetable, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 5
>> yield: 5 cups
>> storage_days: 5
>> storage_method: refrigerated
>> reheat: Microwave or serve at room temperature.

Preheat #oven{} to 425F (220C).

Cut @zucchini{2}(into half-moons), @bell peppers{2}(into chunks), @cherry tomatoes{2%cups}, and @red onion{1%small}(into wedges).

Toss vegetables with @olive oil{4%tbsp}, @garlic{4%cloves}(smashed), @dried oregano{1%tsp}, @dried basil{1/2%tsp}, @kosher salt{1%tsp}, and @black pepper{1/2%tsp}.

Spread on #sheet pans{} in single layer.

Roast ~{25-30%minutes} until tender and slightly charred.

Garnish with @fresh basil{}.

-- Mediterranean vegetables perfect for pasta, bowls, or sides
